<section class="card" id="protect">
<h2><span class="num">9</span>Auto-Protect — every-tick defense</h2>

<p>Once you're in a trade, <code>AutoProtectProfit</code> runs on <strong>every single tick</strong>.
This is the layered defense system that turns small wins into bankings, prevents profitable trades
from going red, and cuts losers fast.</p>

